  <brief_title>Elmex Gel Efficacy in Preventing White Spot Lesions</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 4 Study Prevention of Incipient Carious Lesions (White Spot Lesions) in Patients With Fixed Orthodontic Appliances Following the Application of Elmex Gel</official_title>
